&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I have not tested the heals in WoS solo, but I have seen my pet hold agro on adds even with heals from me or another player since the 12/5 patch. I dont see this as an issue that would affect beastlords in current content at all because our pets really cant offtank and losing the beastlord's dps to keep a pet alive with chain heals in not an option. Generally, I will get agro on the original mob and engage the add with protective spirit on and hope that my healer can keep me alive to beat down one of the mobs and then focus on the original mob.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
